```
**Solution 3: [@NotFound(action = NotFoundAction.IGNORE)][3] with [LEFT JOIN FETCH][4]**
&lt;br&gt;Define ignore `@NotFound` annotation
```java
    @NotFound(action = NotFoundAction.IGNORE)
    @ManyToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
